  "notes": "Fiscal year ended March 31, 2021 but audit was not signed until December 12, 2022 - significant delay. Consolidated entity includes CMHC Housing as fully consolidated subsidiary. Four GBEs accounted for on modified equity basis. Large unexpended ISC deferred revenue of $11.9M and large prior-year unexpended funds transferred into revenue ($9.78M) significantly inflate reported revenue. Net revenue excluding unexpended transfers would be much lower. Equity losses from GBEs of $1.28M recorded. Restricted cash includes capital projects ($8.88M) and CMHC reserve ($861K). Long-term debt includes CIBC and First Nations Bank loans totalling $3.42M plus CMHC mortgages of $5.99M."
